{"tid":1255449,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[官方外掛] 玩家可以開啟「能力值全滿」盡情耍帥！ 《FF8高清版》追加機能公開！","createTime":"2019-06-24T13:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T03:25:48.000Z","uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9a92fba842a58523dea29e8dc684064731b47e07","tid":1255449,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://greatgame.asia/能力值全滿盡情耍帥！-《ff8高清版》追加機能公開/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2F%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E5%80%BC%E5%85%A8%E6%BB%BF%E7%9B%A1%E6%83%85%E8%80%8D%E5%B8%A5%EF%BC%81-%E3%80%8Aff8%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E7%89%88%E3%80%8B%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E6%A9%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%2F&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRohk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=e6984e55\" target=\"_blank\">https://greatgame.asia/能力值全滿盡情耍帥！-《ff8高清版》追加機能公開/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>能力值全滿盡情耍帥！ 《FF8高清版》追加機能公開</ins></strong><br />\nedwardjamjam<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img923/6710/Jf0RWP.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg923%2F6710%2FJf0RWP.jpg%3F&h=95c7ff8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在E3 2019公佈的《最終幻想VIII高清重製版(Final Fantasy VIII Remastered)》，製作人北瀨佳範在近日的一次訪談中，提到遊戲將會追加以下新內容。<strong><ins>這些設定都可由玩家決定開啟與否，方便不論新舊玩家去體驗《FF8》的故事。當中包括「戰鬥三倍加速」、「生命值及ATB值保持全滿」、「特殊技可無限使出」以及「不會在地圖遇上隨機戰鬥」等等</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/001-5.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F001-5.jpg%3F&h=3a363d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>然而PC版更有獨家的設定項目，例如「獲得全部道具、技能及特殊技」；「遊戲貨幣Gil及魔法值升至最高」。</ins></strong>官方暫未解釋為何平台間會有以上差異，但遊戲預計會在2019年內推出，玩家可根據自己的喜好去選擇PC(在Steam上發售)或PS4、Xbox One以及任天堂Switch版本了。"},{"pid":"ae4577db297afe6ba7fc460f9947e324ba6dd90f","tid":1255449,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"<i